Beekeeping: From Ancient History to Modern Practice
In this special episode, Steve Guerra presents a comprehensive history and background on beekeeping, starting with the earliest known apiaries and moving to modern practices. He discusses the evolution of the honeybee, references to honey in ancient texts, and provides insights into the daily life of a beekeeper...
